subTitle: Finding Motivation
category: "life"

there was a holiday in buddhajayenti and I took a leave for day after from office resulting in 4 days off from office including weekends. Since It would take a whole day to reach Pokhara from Kathmandu , I had already wasted my two days of my short vacation. I packed my kindle with
Paulo Coelo for a reread during my trip. I have been getting recommendation of
